      <title>美国和加拿大将就潜在石油资源丰富的北极海床边界进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-canada-to-negotiate-boundary-to-potentially-oil-rich-arctic-seabed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和加拿大已同意就北极海床的主权问题展开谈判。北极海床可能蕴藏着丰富的石油，随着俄罗斯和中国加强在北极地区的存在，该海床的战略重要性也日益提高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-canada-to-negotiate-boundary-to-potentially-oil-rich-arctic-seabed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国财政部长计划加税以解决赤字问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/french-finance-chief-plans-new-taxes-to-tackle-deficit-situation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新任财政部长安托万·阿尔芒 (Antoine Armand) 表示，法国政府正在研究针对富人和大公司征收定向税，以在不取消总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 的促增长改革措施的情况下解决紧急财政问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/french-finance-chief-plans-new-taxes-to-tackle-deficit-situation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党的商业推动未能缓解对政策无效的怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/labour-s-uk-business-push-fails-to-ease-worries-over-policy-void</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国企业对首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 有一个主要担忧：在他上任近三个月后，有关其领导的新工党政府计划如何提振英国经济的细节仍然很少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/labour-s-uk-business-push-fails-to-ease-worries-over-policy-void</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 20:11:21 GMT</pubDate>
